            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan or wok (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chicken thigh</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1607610753861-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
